practitioner.about:
Ms. Sana Faiyaz Ahmed is a Physiotherapist at the Palm Jumeirah branch of Medcare Medical Centre. She has done her BPT and Master's in Neuro-musculoskeletal Physiotherapy. She is certified in NDT & Bobath Techniques, Vestibular Dysfunction and Pelvic Floor Dysfunction, and Basic Life Support. She also holds a Diploma in Human Nutrition. She is a member of the Indian Association of Physiotherapy.

Ms. Ahmed had worked at the Marina branch of Medcare before moving to the Palm Jumeirah branch. She practices Occupational and Physical Therapy which are two types of rehabilitative care. These improve a patient’s quality of life by addressing the different aspects of physical health and daily functioning.

Her expertise covers dry needling and cupping therapy, Kinesiology taping, and manual release and manipulation therapy. She treats musculoskeletal and sports injuries, pre and post-surgical rehabilitation, neuro-muscular rehabilitation, joint pains, TMJ rehabilitation, cardio-pulmonary rehabilitation and pelvic floor rehabilitation, and performs gait analysis, ergonomics and posture correction. She treats both adults and paediatrics and is interested in women’s health and pain management.

In her spare time, Ms. Ahmed enjoys travelling, catching up on her reading and listening to music. She speaks English, Hindi and Marathi.

locations.about:
Medcare Medical Centre in Palm Jumeirah stands as a premium, advanced healthcare facility devoted to meeting the diverse healthcare needs of its community. This inviting medical centre prioritizes comfort and convenience, providing cutting-edge facilities and comprehensive medical services all under one roof.

Ideal for patients of every age seeking precise diagnoses and prompt treatment across various specialties.

At the helm of Medcare Medical Centre Palm Jumeirah is a team of multicultural, multilingual doctors, complemented by exceptionally-trained and experienced nurses and medical staff. The centre takes pride in its extensive array of state-of-the-art equipment, empowering its highly skilled medical team to deliver a premium level of care to all patients.
Experience the warmth of family-centric care delivered by our highly talented medical and non-medical staff. At Medcare Medical Centre Palm Jumeirah, we offer a range of services, including Internal Medicine, Gynaecology, Paediatrics, Dermatology & Aesthetics, ENT, General Medicine, Orthopaedics & Physiotherapy and Radiology. As part of our commitment to accessible healthcare, Medcare operates a network of four hospitals and 20 plus multi-specialty clinics across Dubai and Sharjah. Our goal is to provide reliable and timely medical care to our diverse
clientele.
